songs.title: 339 brah!
songs.lyrics: Im 339 brah, you dont wanna mess. You weigh 89 ponds so stop pumpin out ya chest Ill knock you in your teeth keep you rollin in the sea, we see the fear in oyur eyes lookin like you saw a goose, cuz i got ten chainz on my neck niggas you haterz wish it was a noose, im talking roick ross, talking ray charles, cuz guess what nigga i got eight balls!
